{
  "texts": [
    "Ozer et al.",
    "52 applied a resnet50 deep neural network to analyze cytological images taken during surgery.",
    "Twenty-five medical images from squash smear slides were used in the study.",
    "These images showed samples of non-neoplastic brain tissue as well as high-grade and low-grade gliomas, as well as metastatic carcinomas.",
    "5-fold cross-validation was used for the neural network's training and assessment."
  ]
}